column4: what do these messages mean in my dmesg? "ext3_orphan_cleanup: deleting unreferenced inode 1571906" I've got about 20 of 'em
What ye need is a dapper-testing repository - any chance of that ever happening?
well dapper-testing would be for packages that will (soon) become part of dapper, so we don't get mess-ups like the recent xorg xserver one
